{
  "message": "test(fuzz): add 12 structured dtype corpus seeds\n\nExtends the structured_dtype fuzz target with seeds covering:\n- Subarrays (1D and 2D shapes)\n- Nested structured types\n- Aligned structures with explicit offsets\n- Title descriptors\n- Datetime/timedelta dtypes\n- Boolean type with integer field\n- Void padding fields\n- Big/little/native endian mix\n- Long field names\n- Unicode strings and byte strings\n- Zero-size shape arrays\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
